===Vowels=== ǂAkhoe Haiǁom has a total of 12 vowel phonemes. These can be divided into monophthongs and diphthongs, with a further subdivision into oral and nasal pronunciation.
;Monophtongs: {{IPA|/i e a o u/}} and {{IPA|/ĩ ã ũ/}}.
;Diphthongs: {{IPA|/ai au/}} and {{IPA|/ãi ãu/}}.
